      <p class="lede">When AGYL goes live in your tenant, three things sit inside it. The platform that does the work. The context graph that encodes how your business decides things. And the IP that gets it running — connectors, vertical libraries, the methodology proven in production. <b>The longer it all runs, the sharper your AI gets.</b></p>

